type: Tutorial Step - Help Us With a Star!

definition.text: Giving Superalgos a star on GitHub helps more developers find us, as stars improve the GitHub search rankings!

paragraphs.text: This token of appreciation is not only welcomed by the whole Community, but helps you directly too! The more developers contribute to the project, the better Superalgos gets, and the better it may serve you... so it's a no-brainer!
Just go back to our repository and click the Star button on the top-right corner!
Here's a link for your convenience! Thank you!->github.com/Superalgos/Superalgos
